p: In addition, it has to be considered that other ingredients in the experimental diets could contribute to the trace element contents. Examples are the yellow corn meal and the mineral and vitamin premix. It has to be considered that if the composition of the premix should be altered upon substitution of the soybean meal with the two investigated insect meals, respectively, the lower iron content of both insect meals could require a higher iron content in the premix in comparison to the soybean meal.
